data.description: Welcome home to a tastefully remodeled 4 bedroom, 2 full bath home with a fully detached bonus studio that creates endless possibilities. Featuring all new stainless-steel appliances, quartz countertops, floating shelves and recessed lighting throughout just to name a few! Pull into your extra long driveway for plenty of off street parking and enjoy a fully paid solar system. Conveniently located within walking distance to the park, schools, public transportation and just minutes away from the I-880 and Westfield Shopping Center. Sidewalk Certificate and Sewer compliance complete.
